unnecessary steps (like encoders or imputers), selecting preprocessing methods (e.g., MaxAbsScaler, GenericUnivariateSelect), and estimating performance to guide the search. Finally, 
it constructs the optimized pipeline by pruning optional steps, finalizing preprocessing and feature selection, and preparing the classifier for selection.


